FORMAT: 1A

# Artists Project

## Artists Collection [/artists]

### Fetch an artist with full details [GET]

+ Request (application/json)


+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "artist": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Green Day",
                    "born_at":  "1987-01-01"
                    "albums": [{
                      "name": "Dookie",
                      "released_at": "1999-12-12"
                     }]
                }
            }

### Create an artist [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "artist": {
                "name": "Green Day",
                "born_at": "1987-01-01"
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "artist": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Green Day",
                    "born_at":  "1987-01-01"
                }
            }

### Create an artist with bulk albums [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "artist": {
                "name": "Green Day",
                "born_at": "1987-01-01",
                "albums_attributes": [{
                   "name": "Dookie",
                   "released_at": "1999-12-12"
                }]
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "artist": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Green Day",
                    "born_at":  "1987-01-01"
                }
            }

## Update and Delete artists [/artists/:artist_id/]

### Delete artist [DELETE]

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 204

### Update artist [PUT]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "artist": {
                "name": "Offspring",
                "born_at": "1999-12-12"
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "artist": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Offspring",
                    "born_at":  "1999-12-12"
                }
            }

### update an artist and editing or deleting its albums[POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "artist": {
                "albums_attributes": [{
                   "id": 1
                   "name": "Dookie",
                   "released_at": "1999-12-12"
                },
                {
                  "id": 2,
                  "_destroy": "1"
                }]
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "artist": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Green Day",
                    "born_at":  "1987-01-01"
                }
            }

## Albums Collection [/artists/:artist_id/albums]

### Fetch an album with full details [GET]

+ Request (application/json)


+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "album": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Dookie",
                    "released_at":  "1987-01-01",
                    "artist": {
                      "name": "Green Day",
                      "born_at": "1987-12-12"
                    },
                    "songs": [{
                      "id": 1,
                      "name": "basket case",
                      "track_number": 1,
                      "duration": "1:00",
                     }]
                }
            }

### Create an Album [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "album": {
                "name": "Some name",
                "released_at": "1999-12-12"
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "album": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "some_name",
                    "released_at":  "1999-12-12"
                }
            }
            
### Create an album with bulk songs [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "album": {
                "name": "Dookie",
                "songs_attributes": [{
                   "name": "basket case",
                   "duration": 60,
                   "track_number": 1
                }]
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "album": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Dookie",
                    "released_at": "1999-12-12"
                }
            }

## Update and Delete albums [/artists/:artist_id/albums/:id]

### Delete album [DELETE]

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 204

