                }
            }

## Songs Collection [/artists/:artist_id/albums/:album_id/songs]

### Fetch a song with full details [GET]

+ Request (application/json)


+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "song": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Green Day",
                    "born_at":  "1987-01-01"
                    "albums": [{
                      "name": "Dookie",
                      "released_at": "1999-12-12"
                     }]
                }
            }

### Create a song [POST]


+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "song": {
                "name": "Basket Case",
                "track_number": 1,
                "duration": 60
            }
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            
            {
                "song": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Basket Case",
                    "track_number": 1,
                    "duration": "1:00",
                    "album": {
                      "name": "Dookie",
                      "released_at": "1999-12-12" 
                    }
                }
            }

